\ip \bd ?Nar…ôyen r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai?\bd* Japta infamien kape Ol Wok ramni m…ô n…®p…®g gavman kape Rom r…®m…®rapt…ôr…ôk…®n Pol apa Rom, k…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien in ye kalabus; k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn …ôm…ô in ye kafan nim…ô, k…®ni mobael m…®n…ô k…®m…®sarha tukun apaik…®n, masar…ô iri…ô min, m…ô in tukr…®p…ôh napien. K…®ni ai, gavman r…®mnher-yerhav k…®n, in r…ôriw…ôk …ôm…ô kape newk k…®raru. M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e 2 Timoti, gavman kape Rom r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn m…®n in ye kalabus. Kalabus a ik…®n rahas p…®k ik…®n. M…ôr…®g Ol Wok r…ôp…ôh n…ôvsaoyen k…®n nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a. N…®p…®g n…ôkw…ôkw…ô a r…®mnor ta infamien, nar…®mnar a r…®pior. Kalabus a in r…ôut…ôn ik…®n, k…®ni r…®skai tuk narmam…ô tuk n…®v…ônien m…®vaag p…ôn k…®n. Luk …ôm…ô iriu min. M…ôr…®g Pol rorkeikei m…ô Timoti tukru…ô m…ôm in meinai in kafan fren atuatuk. K…®ni morkeikei m…ô Timoti tukr…®p…®k n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô kafan mu…ô.
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha?\bd* Pol r…®rkun m…ô p…ôh nien m…ô tuktu gavman tukrhopni in. Ror m…ôkneik…®n in r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk n…ôr…ôhu-p…ônien nim…ôhuak ye kwerm…® n…ômehu…ô p…®s…®n m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n r…ômhen k…®n Timoti. N…®p…®g …ôut…ôn m…®n…ô kamhau…ô tuk nim…ôhuak, k…®ni Pol rorkeikei m…ô Timoti tukramrapt…ôr…ôk…®n N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô, k…®ni m…ôrer t…®mt…®m ye nhat…ôt…ôyen kafan, k…®ni m…®p…ôh n…®g…®nien k…®n n…®ni-…ôrhavyen N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô, m…ôrer matuk tuk n…ôr…®gien n…ômh…ôyen ye n…®pran tukm…ô nahasien ru…ô.
\c 1
\s1 Pol r…®m…ô n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, ramv…ôn k…®mi Timoti
\pi1 
\v 1 Timoti. Yo Pol. Kughen r…®m…®rpen-ta yo m…ô yo aposol k…®rik kape Yesu Kristo. K…®ni mher-p…ô k…®n yo m…ô jakni-…ôrhav promes kafan kape n…®mraghien rer…®n ye Yesu Kristo.
\v 2 Yakamrai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®mik, Timoti. Timoti, ik nar…®k yame yakorkeikei p…®k. P…ôh Kughen, R…®mtaw…ô, m…®ne Yesu Kristo Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô, iriu tukrav…ôhsi-pre n…®huv…ôyen, m…®ne norkeikeiyen m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuyen k…®mik.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Wok 16:1; 1 Tim 1:2 \x*
\s1 Pol rav…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®gien kape Timoti
\p 
\v 3 N…®p…®g m-fam, yenp…®g m…®ne yeraan, yakam…ôhuak tuk ik, k…®ni mamni vi vi Kughen tuk ik. K…®ni yo, yakor wok kafan r…ômhen k…®n yame r…®p…®k m…®n…ô k…®m…®sor, k…®ni yak…®rkun m…ô norien has k…®rik r…®rk…ôk irak.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Wok 23:1 \x*
\v 4 R…®kik ram…ôs…®k nehe n…®mr…®m, k…®ni yakorkeikei p…®k m…ô jak…ôm m…®n ik, p…ôh r…®kik tukragien.
\v 5 R…®kik ram…ôs…®k nhat…ôt…ôyen …ôfrak…®s kafam, r…ômhen k…®n yame kafam kaha e Loes m…®ne n…®s…®n…®m e Yunis k…®m…®r…®v…ôh. K…®ni yak…®rkun m…ô takt…ôkun ai, ik m…®n nakav…ôh nhat…ôt…ôyen a.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Wok 16:1 \x*
\v 6 Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-pre n…®rkunien k…®mik tuk norien wok kafan n…®p…®g y…®mn…ôr…ôhu-pre kwerm…®k iram. K…®ni, yakamuh r…®kim m…ô takher nap yerkim tuk norien wok a.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Tim 4:14 \x*
\v 7 Meinai Kughen r…®m…®p…ôh norien r…®kitaw…ô r…®g…®n, m…ôr…®g r…®mnor r…®kitaw…ô m…ô tukram…ôtgah, mamorkeikei, mamor norien yam…ô m…®ne in r…®rkun m…ô k…®satuatuk.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Rom 8:15 \x*
\p 
\v 8 K…®ni m…ôr…®g ik, takp…ôh naur…®sien tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen Yesu Yermaru, k…®ni m…®p…ôh naur…®sien k…®n yo yame k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn yo ye kalabus tuk nhag…®n. Yakam…ôr…®g n…ômh…ôyen tuk N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen. K…®ni Kughen tukr…®v…ôhsi-pre n…ôsan…®nien k…®mik, takam…ôkeikei mor r…ômhen k…®n yame yo yakamor.
\q1 
\v 9 Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôtaw…ô mokr…ôn k…®n …ôtaw…ô tuk n…®mraghien yame ratuatuk, k…®ni nar a, p…ôh nien m…ô nar k…®rik yame k…®taw…ô kasor.
\q2 M…ôr…®g In ramor ye kafan atuk n…ôt…ôr…®gien, m…®ne n…®huv…ôyen kafan.
\q1 N…®p…®g r…®m…®p…ôh nor-han…ôyen tokrei tan…ô,
\q2 m…ôr…®g In r…®m…®rpen-ta Yesu Kristo m…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ô n…®huv…ôyen a.\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Efes 2:8-9; Taet 3:5 \x*
\q1 
\v 10 M…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, In r…®mnor …ôpu n…®huv…ôyen a k…®mi …ôtaw…ô ye nu…ôyen kape Yesu Kristo, yame r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôtaw…ô.
\q2 In r…®mnor t…ôkun n…®mh…ôyen ye n…ôsan…®nien kafan, m…®v…ôhsi-p…ô N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen, yame ramhajoun …ôtaw…ô k…®n n…®mraghien rer…®n.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Hib 2:14 \x*
\p 
\v 11 K…®ni Kughen r…®m…®rpen yo m…ô yo y…ôgkiar k…®rik, m…®ne aposol, m…®ne yhajoun, m…ô jakni-…ôrhav N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô a.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1 Tim 2:7 \x*
\v 12 Ror p…ôn, yakam…ôr…®g p…®k n…ômh…ôyen ye n…®prak tukun. M…ôr…®g yakp…ôh naur…®sien, meinai yakw…®rkun-ta m…ô Pa e yakamhat…ôt…ô iran. M…®rkun huv…ô m…ô In r…®rkun narha-huv…ôyen tuk naha nhag…®n yame In r…®mn…ôr…ôhu-p…ô ye kwerm…®k mamv…ôn meriaji N…®p…®g Kwas…®g.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Swatuk p…®s…®n k…®rik tuk nukrek…®n-ien v. 12: ‚ÄúM…®rkun huv…ô m…ô In r…®rkun narha-huv…ôyen naha nhag…®n yame yo yakam…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ye kwerm…®n m…®v…ôn meriaji N…®p…®g Kwas…®g.‚Äù\f*
\p 
\v 13 Timoti, tak…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n nhajounien atuatuk kafak, m…®kwas…®g k…®n swatuk k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, mamrapt…ôr…ôk…®n nhat…ôt…ôyen m…®ne norkeikeiyen yame rams…®-p…ôn tuk Yesu Kristo.
\v 14 Nanm…®n kape Kughen yame ramar…ô yerkitaw…ô tukramasitu iram, m…ô takarha-huv…ô tuk nar huv…ô yame Kughen r…®mn…ôr…ôhu-pre ye kwerm…®m.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt 1 Tim 6:20 \x*
\s1 Pol ramni vi vi Onesiforas
\p 
\v 15 Timoti, ik nak…®rkun m…ô yo m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n apa kw…ônmhan a Tarki, iri…ô kw…ôr…ô mir e Fugelas m…®ne Hemogenes, iri…ô m-fam kw…ôsapitan k…®n yo.
\p 
\v 16 M…ôr…®g p…ôh Yesu Yermaru tukr…®v…ôh-sip…ôn norkeikeiyen k…®mi Onesiforas m…®ne kafan m…®n…ô. Meinai n…®p…®g r…®psaah, r…®namasitu irak m…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®gien kafak. K…®ni m…®p…ôh naur…®sien m…ô k…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn yo ye kalabus.
\v 17 N…ôfra, n…®p…®g in r…®mau…ô Rom, mamarhak…®n yo, marhak…®n mu…ô meriaji-p…ô m…ôm yo.
\v 18 K…®ni nak…®rkun m…®n m…ô in r…®mnasitu p…®k ye nar…®mnar r…®psaah apa Efesas. !P…ôh Yesu Yermaru tukr…®v…ôh-sip…ôn norkeikeiyen k…®min ye N…®p…®g Kwas…®g!
\c 2
\s1 Norien kape mobael huv…ô kape Yesu Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Timoti, nar…®k, p…ôh Kughen tukror r…®kim r…ôsan…®n ye n…®huv…ôyen yame rams…®-p…ôn ye Yesu Kristo.
\v 2 Nakn…ôr…®g-ta nhajounien kafak yam…ô yakav…ôhsi-…ôrhav ye n…®mr…® narmam…ô khapsaah. V…ôh nhajounien en, m…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ye kwerm…® narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yam…ô m…®ne narmam…ô kashat…ôt…ô ir…ôri…ô, m…ô iri…ô tukharkun n…®shajounien narmam…ô m…®n…ô m…®n t…®ks…®n k…®n.
\v 3 N…®p…®g nahasien ramu…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô, takam…ôkeikei m…ôrer t…®m t…®m r…ômhen k…®n mobael huv…ô k…®rik kape Yesu Kristo.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt 2 Tim 1:8 \x*
\v 4 R…ômhen k…®n mobael k…®rik to rap…ôh norien nar…®mnar yame narmam…ô apnap…®g kasor, m…ôr…®g in ramor …ôm…ô n…ôkwai kapten kafan.
\v 5 R…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô yame ramaiyu m…ô tukrapita m…®v…ôh n…ôrok iran, tukram…ôkeikei m…ôri-p…ôn fam loa m…®n…ô kape naiyuyen, tam…ô r…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhyen n…ôrok iran.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt 2 Tim 4:8 \x*
\v 6 Ratuatuk …ôm…ô m…ôkneik…®n, m…ô yermam…ô yame ramor p…®k wok ye n…ôsimien, in tukr…ôkup…ôn m…®v…ôh kw…ônkwan.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt 1 Kor 9:7 \x*
\v 7 Rhuv…ô m…ô r…®kim tukram…ôs…®k n…ôgkiarien kafak, meinai Yesu Yermaru tukrasitu iram tuk n…®rkunien n…®prai n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô e.
\p 
\v 8 R…®kim tukram…ôs…®k kw…ôn…ôr…ôus k…®rik kape King Deved, Yesu Kristo, In a Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh In ye n…®mh…ôyen kafan. K…®ni in e N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô yame yakamni-…ôrhav.\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Rom 1:3; 1 Kor 15:4 \x*
\v 9 M…ôr…®g kamor yo yakam…ôr…®g n…ômh…ôyen tuk N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô a, kamark…®s-…ôt…ôr…®k…®n yo k…®n jen r…ômhen k…®n yem…ô has k…®rik. M…ôr…®g keinein nark…®s-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n-ien N…ôgkiarien kape Kughen.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt Efes 3:1,13; Fil 1:12-14 \x*
\v 10 Ror m…ôkneik…®n m…ô yakam…ôrer t…®m t…®m ye n…ômh…ôyen m…®n…ô fam tuk narmam…ô yam…ô m…®n…ô Kughen r…®m…®rpen …ôri…ô, m…ô Yesu Kristo tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôri…ô, tuksar…ô iri…ô Kughen ye n…®khakien kafan kape rer…®n.
\p 
\v 11 N…ôgkiarien e ram…ôfrak…®s m…ô,
\q1 Tukm…ô k…®taw…ô khau…ô k…®rikian…ô ye Yesu Kristo ye n…®mh…ôyen kafan,
\q2 k…®ni In tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh m…®n …ôtaw…ô.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt 2 Kor 4:11 \x*
\q1 
\v 12 Tukm…ô kas…ôrer t…®mt…®m,
\q2 k…®ni k…®taw…ô tuksarmaru k…®taw…ô min.
\q1 Tukm…ô k…®taw…ô khaukrek…®n-p…ôn n…®metaitaw…ô k…®min,
\q2 K…®ni In tukrukrek…®n-p…ôn n…®meitaan k…®mi …ôtaw…ô.\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Mat 10:33 \x*
\q1 
\v 13 Tukm…ô k…®taw…ô kas…ôkap…®r pawk n…ôgkiarien kafan,
\q2 m…ôr…®g In tukram…ôkeikei mor, meinai In to rap…ôh nakap…®rien kafan n…ôgkiarien.\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Rom 3:3-4; Taet 1:2 \x*
\s1 Norien atuatuk kape nhajounien N…ôgkiarien kape Kughen
\p 
\v 14 Takuh r…®ki narmam…ô k…®n n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô e. K…®ni mamor kwir…®g k…®mi …ôri…ô ye n…®mr…® Kughen m…ô iri…ô tukhap…ôh n…®sotgohyen tuk n…ôgkiarien apnap…®g. K…®sotgoh, r…®p…ôh nasituyen ye yermam…ô k…®rik; m…ôr…®g ramoriah …ôm…ô narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt 1 Tim 6:4; Taet 3:9 \x*
\v 15 Arkut skai m…ô norien kafam tukrhuv…ô, r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô yame ravhir…ôk…®n nar, yam…ô to rap…ôh naur…®sien tuk kafan norien. Tukm…ô n…®p…®g Kughen r…ôm kafam wok, In r…®rkun neighanien k…®n, meinai nakamhajoun atuatuk n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôfrak…®sien.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Tim 4:6 \x*
\v 16 Ap…ôh k…®ni marer isok tuk n…ôgkiarien yam…ô m…®ne n…®prairi…ô r…®rk…ôk, m…®ne yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh nhasiaiyen Kughen, meinai narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôgkiar m…ôkna, kamhav…ôn isok p…®k tuk Kughen.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*
\v 17 K…®ni nhajounien kap…ôri…ô r…ômhen k…®n n…®map pien k…®rik yame ram…ômhir, mamehu…ô p…®k. Kw…ôr…ô mir k…®raru ir…ôri…ô: Haemeneus m…®ne Faelitas.\x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 Tim 1:20 \x*
\v 18 Iriu k…®m…®rav…ôn isok tuk n…ôfrak…®sien, mar…ôni m…®r…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúKughen r…®mnor ta narmam…ô kamhamragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen, k…®ni to r…®p…ôh nor-m…®n-ien ir…ôtaw…ô tuk n…®p…®g k…®rik.‚Äù Kw…ôr…ô mir ai kworiah nhat…ôt…ôyen kape narmam…ô t…®ks…®n.
\v 19 M…ôr…®g nar apnap…®g …ôm…ô, s…ôpaag ye nim…ô yame Kughen r…®mn…ôr…®p ram…ôrer t…®m t…®m. K…®ni r…®m…®rai-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®rik iran m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúKughen Yermaru r…®rkun narmam…ô kafan m…®n…ô,‚Äù\rq (Nam 16:5)\rq* m…®ne, ‚ÄúNarmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhani mham…ô iri…ô narmam…ô kape Yermaru, tukas…ôkeikei m…®sap…ôh norien has m…®n…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:19 \xt Nam 16:5; Aes 52:11; Jon 10:14; 1 Kor 8:3 \x*
\p 
\v 20 ∆ét…ôr…®g-ru. Ye nim…ô kape yermam…ô yame kafan naut…ô r…®psaah, plet m…®ne besin p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô khapsaah. Kamor t…®ks…®n k…®n gol, t…®ks…®n k…®n silva, t…®ks…®n k…®n nai, t…®ks…®n k…®n kapier. Kamp…®k t…®ks…®n, kam…ôtu-p…ôn nar huv…ô …ôm…ô iran. Kamp…®k t…®ks…®n, kam…ôtu-p…ôn n…®r…ôs…®g iran.
\v 21 R…ômhen k…®n narmam…ô. Tukm…ô k…®hvi-ta n…®r…ôs…®g yerkiri…ô, khau…ô m…®s…ômhen k…®n plet u…ô besin yame kam…ôtu-p…ôn nar huv…ô iran. K…®satuatuk, mharkun n…®sorien wok ehu…ô kape Kughen. Masarer matuk tuk norien nar huv…ô m…®n…ô.
\p 
\v 22 Aiyu m…®v…ôn isok tuk norien has yam…ô m…®ne kamhaur…ô yerki n…®tamaru…ô. K…®ni mam…ôri-p…ôn huv…ô swatuk kape norien yame ratuatuk, m…®ne nhat…ôt…ôyen, m…®ne norkeikeiyen, m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuyen. ∆éri-p…ôn swatuk a k…®mi…ô narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne nakasaiyoh Yesu Yermaru k…®n nasituyen, yerkimi…ô yame rhuv…ô.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt 1 Tim 6:11 \x*
\v 23 Ap m…®v…ôn isok tuk n…ôgkiarien …ôt…ôwao yam…ô m…®ne n…®prairi…ô r…®rk…ôk. N…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô e kamhavi-p…ô …ôm…ô t…®m…ôt tuk notgohyen.\x - \xo 2:23 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*
\v 24 M…ôr…®g yorwok k…®rik kape Yesu Yermaru tukr…®p…ôh notgohyen, m…ôr…®g tukram…ôkeikei mor huv…ô p…ôn k…®mi narmam…ô m-fam, k…®ni tukram…ôkeikei mu…ô r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô kape nhajounien, kafan n…ôt…ôr…®gien tukrapomh.
\v 25 K…®ni tukm…ô narmam…ô t…®ks…®n kamhani hah kafan nhajounien, in tukram…ôkeikei meiwaiyu, mam…ôvhag k…®mi …ôri…ô. Tukm…ô ror Kughen tukreighaan k…®n …ôri…ô m…ô iri…ô tuksarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô hah, m…ô iri…ô tukharkun n…ôfrak…®sien.
\v 26 P…ôh iri…ô tukhau…ô m…®n ye n…ôt…ôr…®gien huv…ô, k…®ni m…®s…ôta ye kw…ônm…ôkuru kape Setan, yame ramrapt…ôr…ôk…®n …ôri…ô, kasor n…ôkwan.
\c 3
\s1 Kwas…®g ik…®n Yesu tukru…ô m…ôkir narmam…ô, nahasien tukru…ô
\p 
\v 1 K…®ni takam…ôkeikei m…®rkun m…®n nar…®mnar e: N…®p…®g Kwas…®g tukru…ô ipak…ô, n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn m…®n…ô tukhau…ô.\x - \xo 3:1 \xt 1 Tim 4:1 \x*
\v 2 Meinai, narmam…ô tukas…ôr…®g …ôm…ô …ôri…ô, m…®sorkeikei p…®k mane. M…®sausit, mhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk …ôri…ô. Mamhani hah narmam…ô, m…®s…ôs…®k n…ôkwai n…®s…®nri…ô m…®n…ô m…®ne r…®mri…ô m…®n…ô, mhap…ôh nhani-vivi-yen narmam…ô tuk nasituyen, mhap…ôh nhasiaiyen Kughen.
\v 3 Norkeikeiyen kap…ôri…ô tukr…®rk…ôk. Tukhap…ôh n…®s…ôru-k…®nien t…ôvhag…ô hah yam…ô kamor ir…ôri…ô. Tuksoriah nhag narmam…ô. Mhap…ôh n…®sarha-huv…ôyen tuk n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô. R…®kiri…ô tukragien tuk noriahyen yermam…ô. Tuks…ôm…ôk…®n nar huv…ô m…®n…ô.
\v 4 Iri…ô k…ôut k…ôsu…ô m…®n…ô. Tuksor nar…®mnar ye n…ôt…ôwaoyen. Mhav…ôhsihakt…ô atuk …ôri…ô. M…®sorkeikei nar…®mnar tuk n…ôr…®g-huv…ô-yen ye n…®prairi…ô, m…ôr…®g tukhap…ôh n…®sorkeikeiyen Kughen.
\v 5 Tukhas…®g…ôv…®n …ôm…ô n…ôhuakien, mhap…ôh n…®seighanien m…ô Kughen tukr…®v…ôn yerkiri…ô.
\p Yuv…ôn isok tuk narmam…ô kasor m…ôkna\x - \xo 3:5 \xt Mat 7:15,21; Taet 1:16 \x*
\v 6 meinai kamhav…ôn yerkwanu m…®n…ô, masor nar iko tuk nhavi-ta-yen n…ôr…®gien kape n…®piraov…®n yam…ô m…®ne kap…ôri…ô n…ôr…®gien rap…ôh n…®skaiyen. T…ôvhag…ô hah kape n…®piraov…®n m…®n…ô a r…ômhen k…®n kajip…ô pam. R…®kiri…ô r…®v…ôn tuk norien hah, k…®ni ravi-…ôhu …ôri…ô.
\v 7 Iri…ô kas…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n nhajounien p…®s…®n p…®s…®n, m…ôr…®g tukhap…ôh nhaniyen n…ôfrak…®sien ye N…ôgkiarien ∆éfrak…®s kape Kughen tuk n…®p…®g k…®rik.
\p 
\v 8 Apa kup…ôn, kw…ôr…ô mir a Janes m…®ne Jambres\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Eks 7:11, 22, 9:11.\f* k…®maw…ôs…®k n…ôgkiarien kape Moses, k…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, narmam…ô m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n k…®s…ôs…®k n…ôgkiarien …ôfrak…®s kape Kughen. Narmam…ô m…®n…ô a, n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô r…®nahas. Nhat…ôt…ôyen kap…ôri…ô rap…ôh n…ômhenien.
\v 9 M…ôr…®g nhajounien eiku…ô kap…ôri…ô to rap…ôh n…ôrerien ror tu, meinai tukpi…ôm …ôpu n…ôt…ôwaoyen kap…ôri…ô, r…ômhen k…®n kw…ôr…ô mir a Janes m…®ne Jambres.
\s1 M…ô Timoti tukr…ôri-p…ôn norien kape Pol
\p 
\v 10 M…ôr…®g ik, Timoti, nakam…ôri-p…ôn kafak nhajounien, m…®ne norien kape n…®mraghien kafak, m…®ne naha nhag…®n yame yakm…ô jakor, m…®ne kafak nhat…ôt…ôyen, m…®ne n…ôt…ôr…®gien apomh kafak, m…®ne kafak norkeikeiyen, m…®ne n…ôrer-t…®m-t…®mien kafak.
\v 11 Ik nakw…®rkun-ta n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhau…ô ye n…®mraghien kafak, m…®ne norien has yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnor irak. Nak…®rkun norien …ôut…ôn yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnor irak apa Antiok m…®ne Ikoniam m…®ne Listra.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Wok 13:50; 14:5; 14:19\x* M…ôr…®g Yesu Yermaru r…®m…®r…ôhsi-ta yo ye nar…®mnar m-fam a.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Sam 34:19\x*
\v 12 M…ôr…®g, n…ôfrak…®sien: Tukuh narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne kham…ô tuksor k…®rikian…ô iri…ô Yesu Kristo, masor n…ôkwai Kughen.\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Mat 16:24; Jon 15:20; Wok 14:22 \x*
\v 13 K…®ni m…ôr…®g n…ôm…ô has m…®n…ô, m…®ne narmam…ô kape neiku…ôyen, iri…ô tuksor norien has, mhav…ôn, masor yame rahas …ôgk…ôp. Tukameiku…ô ir…ôri…ô, kamhav…ôn maseiku…ô ye narmam…ô.
\p 
\v 14 M…ôr…®g ik, Timoti, ik nakw…®rkun huv…ô ta …ômaw…ô yam…ô m…®ne yakshajoun ik. Ror p…ôn takam…ôkeikei m…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô nar…®mnar yam…ô m…®ne yakshajoun ik k…®n, yam…ô m…®ne nakamni n…ôfrak…®sien ir…ôri…ô.
\v 15 Ye n…ôk…ôsk…ôhyen kafam mu…ô meriaji-p…ô takt…ôkun, nakw…®rkun-ta N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen e yame r…®rkun n…®v…ôhsi-preyen n…®rkunien k…®mik m…ô takhat…ôt…ô ye Yesu Kristo m…ô Kughen tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh ik.
\v 16 N…ôgkiarien m-fam ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen kamhas…®-p…ôn ye n…ôkwai Kughen …ôm…ô, k…®ni m…®sasitu ir…ôtaw…ô. M…®shajoun …ôtaw…ô, mamhani-…ôrhav norien has m…®n…ô kap…ôtaw…ô, mas…ôr…ôhu atuatuk …ôtaw…ô, k…®ni m…®shajoun …ôtaw…ô k…®n norien yam…ô m…®ne k…®satuatuk.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Rom 15:4 \x*
\v 17 K…®sasitu ir…ôtaw…ô m…ôkneik…®n: K…®taw…ô narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô, tukhav…ôh nasituyen m…®n…ô fam a, k…®ni mhau…ô narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kharkun n…®sorien wok huv…ô m…®n…ô m-fam.
\c 4
\nb 
\v 1 Timoti, jakv…ôhsi-pre n…ôgkiarien keikei k…®rik k…®mik ye n…®mr…® Kughen m…®ne Yesu Kristo yame tukru…ô m…ôkir narmam…ô m-fam, iri…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhamragh, m…®ne yam…ô m…®ne kw…ônhamh…ô-ta. Yesu e natukru…ô mamarmaru; ror p…ôn, yakav…ôhsi-pre n…ôgkiarien keikei e m…®m…ô:
\v 2 Ni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen, k…®ni arer matuk tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen, nar apnap…®g m…ô r…®mar …ôm…ô u…ô r…ôut…ôn. ∆ér…ôhu atuatuk norien kape narmam…ô, k…®ni ni-…ôrhav norien has m…®n…ô, k…®ni m…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôt…ôr…®gien kape narmam…ô. Takamor wok m…®n…ô e, kafam n…ôt…ôr…®gien tukrapomh, k…®ni kafam nhajounien tukratuatuk m…®huv…ô.
\v 3 Takam…ôkeikei mor m…ôkneik…®n meinai, n…®p…®g yame ramu…ô, narmam…ô tuks…ôp…ôh n…ôgkiarien atuatuk, m…®s…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô, mamhav…ôh namhajoun p…®s…®n p…®s…®n yam…ô m…®ne kamhani-…ôrhav …ôm…ô n…ôgkiarien yame narmam…ô r…®kiri…ô ragien tukun.\x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Tim 4:1 \x*
\v 4 Tukhaukreik…®n-p…ôn n…®m…ôt…®rg…®ri…ô tuk n…ôgkiarien …ôfrak…®s, mhav…ôn m…®s…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n kwanage eiku…ô m…®n…ô.
\p 
\v 5 M…ôr…®g ik, arha huv…ô tuk kafam n…ôr…®gien n…®p…®g m-fam, nar apnap…®g m…ô nar…®mnar p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô kamhau…ô ye n…®mraghien kafam. N…®p…®g nahasien tukramu…ô tuk ik, takam…ôrer t…®m t…®m. K…®ni yuv…ôn, markurao, mamni-…ôrhav N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô. K…®ni takam…ôkeikei mamor fam wok yame Kughen rav…ôhsi-pre k…®mik m…ô takor.
\p 
\v 6 M…ôr…®g yo, p…ôh nien m…ô tuktu, yakmh…ô. N…®mraghien kafak ruau…ô r…ômhen k…®n nar m…®ragh k…®rik yame k…®vaan …ôru tuk n…®ni-vi-vi-yen Kughen.\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Fil 2:17 \x*
\v 7 Yo, y…®mnamaiyu …ôm…ô tuk nhat…ôt…ôyen ye Kughen, mamaiyu huv…ô meriaji naiyuyen infamien; yakw…ôrapt…ôr…ôk…®n nhat…ôt…ôyen kafak.\x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Tim 6:12 \x*
\v 8 Yermam…ô yame ramaiyu mapita, k…ôvh…ôvhao-p…ôn k…®min r…ômhen k…®n n…ôrok kafan. K…®ni Yesu Yermaru, In ram…ôkir huv…ô narmam…ô, m…ôkir n…®mraghien kafak, m…ô ratuatuk. Mor apn…ôpein…ô tuk n…ôrok kafak. K…®ni p…ôh nien m…ô yo p…®s…®n …ôm…ô, m…ôr…®g tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®sorkeikei mamhawhin m…ô In tukru…ô m…®n.
\s1 Pol ram…ôvsao k…®n kafan m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n
\p 
\v 9 Timoti, arkut skai mhai m…®ren mu…ô m…ôm yo,
\v 10 meinai kw…ôn a Demas rorkeikei p…®k n…®mraghien kape tokrei tan…ô e, marar, mapta k…®n yo, m…®v…ôn apa Tesalonaeka. K…®ni kw…ôn a Kresens ruav…ôn ta apa Galesia\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Tukm…ô ror Kresens r…®mav…ôn apa Spen.\f*, k…®ni Taetas ruav…ôn ta apa Dalmesia.\fig Taon kape Tesalonaeka|alt="Thessalonica" src="HK025D.jpg" size="span" loc="End of 2 tim" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="2TI 4:10"\fig*
\v 11 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, Luk p…®s…®n …ôm…ô ramar…ô k…®mru min. Rhuv…ô m…ô takrau…ô k…®miru Mak, meinai in tukrasitu irak tuk wok kafak.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt Wok 15:37-39; 2 Kor 8:23; Kol 4:14 \x*
\v 12 M…ôr…®g y…®mnher-p…ôn ta k…®n kw…ôn a Tikikas apa Efesas.
\v 13 Tukm…ô n…®p…®g nakamu…ô, takam…ôkeikei m…®r…ôh neip…ôn a yame y…®mn…ôr…ôhu ram…ôm…®r apa imei Kapas, apa Traos. Rhuv…ô m…ô takp…®k m…®n kafak n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô mu…ô. M…®p…ôh n…ôru-k…®nien n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnor k…®n t…®ki n…ôni, m…®p…®k, mu…ô.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt Wok 20:6 \x*
\p 
\v 14 M…ôr…®g kw…ôn a Aleksanda, in yermam…ô kape norien wok ye aean, in r…®mnor rahas-p…ô k…®mi yo. Yesu Yermaru tukr…®v…ôh-sip…ôn tai norien kafan.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Aes 59:18; Rom 2:6 \x*
\v 15 M…ôr…®g ik m…®n takam…ôr…®g ik tuk kw…ôn a, meinai in r…®mnam…ôs…®k p…®k n…ôgkiarien kap…ôtaw…ô.
\p 
\v 16 K…®ni n…®p…®g k…®m…®s…ôkup…ôn m…®s…ôr…®p yo ye kot, y…®m…®ni-…ôrhav n…ôr…®gien kafak, k…®ni yermam…ô r…®rk…ôk tuk neighanien k…®n kafak n…ôgkiarien. M…ôr…®g kafak narmam…ô m…®n…ô k…®m…®sap, m…®s…ôp…ôh yo. (P…ôh Kughen tukr…®p…ôh norien tai norien kap…ôri…ô).
\v 17 M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g a, Yesu Yermaru, In ram…ôm…®r k…®mru min, m…®v…ôhsi-p…ô n…®rkunien k…®mi yo m…ô jakni-…ôrhav huv…ô N…ôgkiarien Kafan, m…ô n…ôm…ô tan…ô p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô tuks…ôr…®g. Yemehu…ô kape kot ipak…ô …ôm…ô r…®m…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ô narp…®nien k…®mi yo m…ô jakam…ôkeikei m…®mh…ô, m…ôr…®g Yesu Yermaru r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh yo.\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Pol r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYesu r…®m…®r…ôhsi-ta yo ye n…ôkwai laeon.‚Äù \f*
\v 18 K…®ni In tukr…®r…ôhsi-ta yo tuk nahasien fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…ô tukor irak. Mamrapt…ôr…ôk…®n huv…ô yo, m…®v…ôh yo m…®v…ôn ye rao ye neai. P…ôh khav…ôh-sihakt…ô In ye newk m…®ne newk kape rer…®n. Amen.
\s1 N…ôgkiarien infamien
\p 
\v 19 Yakamni rhuv…ô tuk Akwila m…®ne piraov…®n kafan Prisila, m…®ne Onesiforas m…®ne kafan m…®n…ô.\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Wok 18:2; 2 Tim 1:16-17 \x*
\v 20 Kw…ôn a r…®mnam…ôm…®r apa Korin. N…®p…®g y…®m…®t…ôrhav apa Maelitas, m…®p…ôh Trofimas ram…ôm…®r, meinai in ramh…ô.\x - \xo 4:20 \xt Wok 19:22; 20:4; Rom 16:23 \x*
\p 
\v 21 Timoti, arkut skai mhai m…®ren mu…ô eik…®n e kwas…®g ik…®n n…®p…®g kape nokieiyen.
\p Yubulas m…®ne Pudens m…®ne Linus m…®ne Klodia, m…®ne n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô fam kamhani rhuv…ô pre tuk ik.
\p 
\v 22 P…ôh Yesu Yermaru tukramar…ô k…®miru min. P…ôh n…®huv…ôyen kape Kughen tukramar…ô tuk …ômi…ô. 
